{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 171300, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哎，今天我一同学的表弟也铁了心想学生物，这个世界咋了？", "timestamp": 1595607831, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "让我想起来前两天对线的dz认为底层人民都是因为道德败坏懒惰，树洞大讨论做题家女孩该不该靠身体上位。理想主义才是我们这个时代最稀缺的东西啊。", "timestamp": 1595607878, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "省前二十也算不上特别高的分，随他去吧", "timestamp": 1595607944, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171313, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得多和他们谈谈其他地方也能有所成就，多谈谈家庭会好点", "timestamp": 1595607985, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171315, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 对于一个普通家庭的孩子来说是改变命运的机会啊。作为学长我还是有必要劝两句的，哪怕他不听", "timestamp": 1595608028, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "叹气。\n还好不是化工。", "timestamp": 1595608651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你说先报好的专业，进去后真的喜欢再转，不知道转化生难不难", "timestamp": 1595609699, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171418, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你给他客观说清化生的就业问题就可以了，选择权在他的手上", "timestamp": 1595611625, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 171572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 30403, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "选择权是别人的，